  "text": "This work uses a custom formalism, similar to temporal testers in e.g. [CITATION_1] , [CITATION_2] , for defining observers to PSL formulae. The custom formalism makes it easy to combine observers for sub-formulae into an observer for the whole formula. They are also relatively simple to convert directly to NuSMV modules.",
